{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a9d020ba80","title":"北京各厂矿企业党委书记提出整风中几个急待解决的问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"462bd63fdd","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":21,"articleId":"a9d020ba80"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"16707e9016","name":"任志樵"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b821f82dfc","type":"title","text":"北京各厂矿企业党委书记提出整风中几个急待解决的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"172f5622f8","type":"authors","text":"任志樵","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"3c25c0784e","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社北京21日讯　在中共北京市委工业部召开的各厂矿企业党委书记会上，提出了整风中几个急待明确和解决的问题：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"ab6dbed4fd","type":"paragraph","text":"一、参加整风的同志，要不要一个一个地“过关”？检查以后，群众还有意见，被批评者又不同意怎么办？要不要找重点人？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"bc59bf0b92","type":"paragraph","text":"二、在一个工厂企业党委会里，是不是每个成员都要单独作思想检查报告？是不是只要党委主要负责人检查并且作检查报告，其他同志作一般检查就行了？","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"e291958a15","type":"paragraph","text":"三、整风中牵涉到工资、福利怎么办？过去不合理的问题，是否可以解决？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"6163b8b2f7","type":"paragraph","text":"四、领导检查以后是否还要交代？向谁交代？是开职工代表大会或党员代表大会交代还是党政工团分别交代？","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"efb25c4eaf","type":"paragraph","text":"五、整风中是否要作出书面检查？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"8f513961c8","type":"paragraph","text":"六、群众对非党负责干部意见多了怎么办？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"8394140564","type":"paragraph","text":"七、工厂企业中只有一个党委书记或厂长，怎么贯彻执行整风生产两不误？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"eb82a70545","type":"paragraph","text":"八、工厂企业中的小报，是否也像人民日报一样什么意见都登？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"76c8bdaeb1","type":"paragraph","text":"九、中央指示中提出反对三个主义，但中中央来提应该树立什么，怎么办？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"9a75a00224","type":"paragraph","text":"十、中央对整风运动有无具体措施？过去“三反”、“肃反”都有百分之几的控制数，这次是否也有？　　(任志樵)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"},{"id":"ce3f760bce","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源： 1957年5月21日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80"}],"page":{"id":"e23202f6ac","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a9d020ba80","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}